{"tid":597232,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"（學英文）有咩卡通好推薦？","createTime":"2018-03-18T12:13:46.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-21T02:12:04.000Z","uid":1369,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"2fa2989a4ced280bfd330694073f358bd809db7c","tid":597232,"uid":1369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T12:13:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"17de1bd326794bb769d32b9878bb35b923eb9111","tid":597232,"uid":3037,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T14:18:55.000Z","msg":"South Park"},{"pid":"3f525a7409aea22536bae589f456b41d98da185a","tid":597232,"uid":109538,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T14:31:46.000Z","msg":"Rick and Morty"},{"pid":"89e6ea2bd2bf0642608355efac0938c61189a477","tid":597232,"uid":7583,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T17:33:23.000Z","msg":"ben10"},{"pid":"787019c3d97344d4c9d9d4b23206897bc255c514","tid":597232,"uid":26506,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"3f525a7409aea22536bae589f456b41d98da185a","tid":597232,"uid":109538,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T14:31:46.000Z","msg":"Rick and Morty"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T18:10:36.000Z","msg":"To be fair, you have to have a very high IQ to understand Rick and Morty. The humour is extremely subtle, and without a solid grasp of theoretical physics most of the jokes will go over a typical viewer&rsquo;s head. There&rsquo;s also Rick&rsquo;s nihilistic outlook, which is deftly woven into his characterisation- his personal philosophy draws heavily from Narodnaya Volya literature, for instance. The fans understand this stuff; they have the intellectual capacity to truly appreciate the depths of these jokes, to realise that they&rsquo;re not just funny- they say something deep about LIFE. As a consequence people who dislike Rick &amp; Morty truly ARE idiots- of course they wouldn&rsquo;t appreciate, for instance, the humour in Rick&rsquo;s existential catchphrase &ldquo;Wubba Lubba Dub Dub,&rdquo; which itself is a cryptic reference to Turgenev&rsquo;s Russian epic Fathers and Sons. I&rsquo;m smirking right now just imagining one of those addlepated simpletons scratching their heads in confusion as Dan Harmon&rsquo;s genius wit unfolds itself on their television screens. What fools.. how I pity them. <br />\n<br />\nAnd yes, by the way, i DO have a Rick &amp; Morty tattoo. And no, you cannot see it. It&rsquo;s for the ladies&rsquo; eyes only- and even then they have to demonstrate that they&rsquo;re within 5 IQ points of my own (preferably lower) beforehand. Nothin personnel kid."},{"pid":"1bc25e7b060864a1d22b81267d2c265184cf4ea0","tid":597232,"uid":6005,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T18:14:54.000Z","msg":"peppa pig<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"abc2e1b307eab56f060a3b7955b05eca464f91c9","tid":597232,"uid":95963,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T18:22:06.000Z","msg":"Bob&rsquo;s Burgers <br />\nMr. Pickles <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8498327770bd76d85eebdcb0d3910cb8bcbb2d1c","tid":597232,"uid":94266,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-18T18:59:09.000Z","msg":"簡單少少就睇遊戲王，G Gundam呢啲。咁當然緊係英文配音啦。主要係畫面靚，又有劇情。<br />\n<br />\n深少少就睇family guy。 美式動畫就好少會靚過日式架啦，不過呢類夠賤夠搞笑既卡通片根本唔洗靠畫面。<br />\n<br />\nrick and morty, South Park, Simpson呢啲都可以睇吓既，不過就唔係咁啱我口味。family guy算係我唯一笑得最多既卡通片。"},{"pid":"8df1be8f423f1042156e534491c49a7fd7f168fb","tid":597232,"uid":2107,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-19T01:36:44.000Z","msg":"Happ tree friends"},{"pid":"d552977d07b78a46772b2e20b8b04c2f42811ba1","tid":597232,"uid":1954,"lik